T01TD1177E:255a-1: shr'i gu ru ba na ratna sto tra sa bta kam / bod skad du /
T01TD1177E:255a-2: dpal ldan bla ma nags kyi rin chen gyi bstod pa bdun pa //
T01TD1177E:255a-3: dpal ldan bla ma nags kyi rin chen gyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1177E:255a-4: bal po'i yul gyi rgyal po bde bar gshegs pa yi //
T01TD1177E:255a-5: lugs la rtag tu rjes su brtson pa la bkod cing //
T01TD1177E:255a-6: mkhas pa rnams kyi mdzod gyur mthar thug yon tan gyi //
T01TD1177E:255a-7: tshogs kyi zab mo snang mdzad dge slong rgyal po ste //
T01TD1177E:255a-8: rnam par grags shing ma chungs pa med pa'i grags pa yi //
T01TD1177E:255a-9: rgyal mtshan bla bre dar dpyangs zab cing rgya che'i blo //
T01TD1177E:255a-10: sku yang sems can rnams kyi skyabs ni gcig pu ste //
T01TD1177E:255a-11: theg chen yang dag rtogs pas grub pa'i mtha' yi mdzod //
T01TD1177E:255a-12: nags kyi rin chen zhes bya sdom brtson mchog gi blo //
T01TD1177E:255a-13: gnas brtan 'di na gnyis med chos kyi de nyid rig /'dul ba'i sdom pas yang dag sdom la mngon par brtson //
T01TD1177E:255a-14: phas rgol glang po'i dbang la ri dags rgyal po lags //
T01TD1177E:255a-15: phyag 'tshal sdom brtson chen po'i rgyal po rnams kyi mchog / mchog gi tshul la rab tu rnam par nges pa skye //
T01TD1177E:255a-16: skye ba sdug bsngal dag las 'byin byed gcig pu mchog / mchog tu nags kyi rin chen gnas brtan chen po lags //
T01TD1177E:255a-17: chags bral sems can ma lus pa dag sad par mdzad //
T01TD1177E:255a-18: phyag gi chu skyes dag gis mtshon gyi gzhu 'chang ba //
T01TD1177E:255a-19: 'dzin pa'i mthil gyi rgyan du gyur pa mdzes pa'i sku //
T01TD1177E:255a-20: gnas brten chen po nags kyi rin chen rab tu mdzes //
T01TD1177E:255a-21: dga' bral dga' ba'i glang po la sog dri ma yi //
T01TD1177E:255b-0: dri ma dri ma @255b med cing bral ba nyams su myong //
T01TD1177E:255b-1: srid dang srid pa ma yin gnyis kyi 'ben la mnga' //
T01TD1177E:255b-2: gnas brtan chen po nags kyi rin chen skyabs su gyur //
T01TD1177E:255b-3: dga' bral dang po'i bdud rtsi'i btud pa bdag la dgyes //
T01TD1177E:255b-4: dgyes shing nges la dul ba'i yan lag brgya phrag gis //
T01TD1177E:255b-5: sems can brgya phrag tshogs rnams yongs su smin pa dag / rtsi mdzad gnas brtan chen po nags kyi rin chen no //
T01TD1177E:255b-6: bdud sde la sogs rnams kyi kha la ro med mdzad //
T01TD1177E:255b-7: kha yi chu skyes dag ni dgra yis gang ba 'dzems //
T01TD1177E:255b-8: skye mched 'dar ba'i phas rgol ri yi dbang po 'khru //
T01TD1177E:255b-9: khrus mdzad nags kyi rin chen gnas brtan chen po'o //
T01TD1177E:255b-10: dpal ldan bla ma nags kyi rin chen gyi bstod pa bdun pa 'di ni rdzogs so /
T01TD1177E:255b-12: // / yul ma ga dh'a nas byung ba'i dge bsnyen dam pa nyi ma pa zhes bya bas mdzad pa'o //
T01TD1177E:255b-13: 'di ni spyan mnga' chos kyi rgyal pos gser gyi me tog dang bcas pa'i bka' lung gis //
T01TD1177E:255b-14: rtse thang lo ts'a ba gzhon nu dpal gyis bsgyur ba'o /
